def jsonRes = messageExchange.getResponse().contentAsString
def jsonSlurper = new groovy.json.JsonSlurper() def parse = jsonSlurper.parseText(jsonRes)
def zipCode = parse.travelAgencies[0].address.postalCode log.info zipCode assert zipCode!=null
def countryCode = parse.travelAgencies[0].address.countryCode log.info countryCode assert countryCode!=null
